snippet.title: New Prince Harry and Meghan Markle film SLAMMED as 'sick' and 'offensive' | Sunrise
snippet.description:
A new movie has sparked outrage among royal fans for depicting Meghan Markle lying injured among the wreckage of an overturned car. The scene.. reminiscent of Princess Diana's death.. has been labelled 'sick' and 'offensive'. While most people are on either Team Royal or Team Sussex.. this film has managed to unite fans of both sides. And they're not keeping quiet about it..
